<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生鏽刀我同你講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你咁樣係唔會令到我地驚架</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁囂張續個續個打電話兇班細 又話無得升又話釘硬ot牌又乜乜漆漆<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最無資格講code of ethics係你呀dllm</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n釘牌<br />\n睇下邊個比人釘牌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己都一大堆黑歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">醫護同行 罷工抗疫</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人 自己地方自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe51af534413951a7c2f259f6ebc109099544b6c","tid":1861212,"uid":259290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:50:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aafd3955fd8949e79ac6ad211267d559cb263aca","tid":1861212,"uid":259290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:52:43.000Z","msg":"繼續罷工"},{"pid":"32eb496c5b3f6ca12d5daee0e7ab9b478ff28d5b","tid":1861212,"uid":7441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"支持！<br />\n生銹刀你收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab186648a7e54232993c32d14aefd7402771f38","tid":1861212,"uid":247992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:40:43.000Z","msg":"支持你哋呀手足"},{"pid":"4895eae67980c8aa9e8f613eb4a2b85e6f9beb06","tid":1861212,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike"